entries.title: Simon Cowell's 'unrecognisable' appearance leaves Royal Variety performance viewers in shock
entries.description: The music mogul, 63, left viewers distracted by his incredibly smooth visage, which may be the result of cosmetic surgery,  with one asking: 'What's he done to himself?'.
